{"tid":2099222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母，我地要將《義勇軍進行曲》個精粹唱到出黎","createTime":"2020-07-08T05:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T05:55:04.000Z","uid":10014,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e852516ab0f41eae94bffd00e2222e70a9b4690","tid":2099222,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄條on9話榮光係右傾<br />\n<br />\n我就將《義勇軍》個精粹發揚光大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起來！<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不願做奴隸的人們</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中華</span>民族到了最危險的時候，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！起來！起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心，<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"be92e9164cadc0f9cc0ecff3b9274249cf1ee203","tid":2099222,"uid":52804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9fd252e591f6dfcb0e41473f2a8ef46cfdbf94ef","tid":2099222,"uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"其實文革版本仲正，擁護緊我地偉大既毛澤東先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前進！各民族英雄的人民！<br />\n偉大的共產黨領導我們繼續長征。<br />\n萬眾一心奔向共產主義明天，<br />\n建設祖國保衛祖國英勇的鬥爭。<br />\n前進！前進！前進！<br />\n我們千秋萬代<br />\n高舉毛澤東旗幟，前進！<br />\n高舉毛澤東旗幟，前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！"},{"pid":"d3c9b8b645209e9898e23f74afe19d5556769511","tid":2099222,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd252e591f6dfcb0e41473f2a8ef46cfdbf94ef","tid":2099222,"uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"其實文革版本仲正，擁護緊我地偉大既毛澤東先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\